		  <h3>Support the Actors Theatre</h3>
		  <p>A non-profit 501(C)(3) organization, The Actors Theatre depends on donations from the Kansas City community. Our donors include corporations, foundations and arts organizations. But more than anything, we rely on people like you with a passion for keeping premiere theatre in Kansas City.</p>
